# Architecture Decision Records (ADR)

## ADR-0001
Clocking

Decision:
All synchronous logic shall use the positive edge of the system clock.

Reason:
Consistency across the entire ForgeAI architecture.

---

## ADR-0002
Reset

Decision:
All synchronous modules shall implement an active-high synchronous reset.

Reason:
Simplifies learning and provides consistent behavior.

---

## ADR-0003
Parameterization

Decision:
Reusable modules shall use parameters where practical.

Reason:
Promotes scalability and reduces duplicated RTL.